OK i just want answers

thats all, I just want straight forward answers no gasping at my noobyness or swearing at me because i dont read other forums,

The whole server is made from coodernates and Pixels and Graphic.

Usually a server provides you with coodernates when you go into run it should say Coodernates
X:####
Y:####
But it will have numbers instead of #'s. Every single square on that game in other words. Where you walk. Contains a Coordernate. I hope this helps and sorry my spelling probably isn’t the best
